    OE[Open-Endedness\nmin hist. NN sim (Eq.3)]
    IL[Illumination\nmin NN across sims (Eq.4)]
  end

  subgraph OPT[Search / Optim]
    O1[Sep-CMA-ES / Evo]
    O2[Genetic (μ+λ)]
    O3[Selection & Archive]
  end

  subgraph AR[Artifacts & UI]
    R[(Artifacts Store\nparams, frames, embeddings, scores)]
    D[Atlas / UMAP / Dashboard]
  end

  C --> V1
  V2 --> T
  V1 --> T
  V1 --> OE
  V1 --> IL

  T --> O1 --> O3
